## Research Attribution

This formalization is based on the research of Professor Eva Miranda (Universitat
Politècnica de Catalunya) and collaborators. The mathematical content originates
from their published works:

- Miranda, E., & Ramos, D. (2025). Classical billiards can compute.
- González-Prieto, Á., Miranda, E., & Peralta-Salas, D. (2025). TKFT as a model of computation.
- Cardona, R., Miranda, E., Peralta-Salas, D., & Presas, F. (2021). Turing complete Euler flows.
- Dyhr, S., González-Prieto, Á., Miranda, E., & Peralta-Salas, D. (2025). Turing complete Navier-Stokes.

See README.md for full citations.
